Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.94,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Takže Oyashirova kliatba?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:08.36,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:10.26,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Vystrašila som ťa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:11.51,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:14.50,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ty si Shion Sonozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.02,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Vy ste priateľka mojej sestry alebo niečo také?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:20.75,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Dalo by sa to tak povedať.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.58,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Volám sa Miyo Takano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:26.57,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Môžeš mi hovoriť Miyo. Dobre, Shion-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.05,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Hneváš sa na mňa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:35.27,Anyone,,0,0,0,,To je škoda. Keď si predstavím čo všetko by sme mohli dokázať ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:39.22,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,To všetko sú len moje dohady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:43.36,Anyone,,0,0,0,,"Oyashirova kliatba" je označenie pre sériu záhadných úmrtí.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.45,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Každé z nich
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:50.41,Anyone,,0,0,0,,vyzerá ako úplne samostatný prípad ale aj napriek tomu majú mnoho spoločné.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:54.94,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Každý rok Oyashiro jednu osobu odsúdi a zabije,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:57.75,Anyone,,0,0,0,,zatiaľ čo druhá zmizne ako obeta preňho.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.42,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Jednu zabije kliatba...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:04.78,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,a druhá... Počkať! Čo ste to vravela?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:05.84,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Skrátka,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:10.32,Anyone,,0,0,0,,množstvo ľudí ktorý zomreli musí byť rovnaké ako ľudí ktorých obetovali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.12,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Obetovali?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:19.16,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Skúmala som dávno zabudnutú históriu Hinamizawi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.89,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Je to temná história.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:25.73,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Pred érou Meiji sa Hinamizawa volala Dedina Onigafuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:29.74,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ty si toho o minulosti Hinamizawi veľa nepočula, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.21,Anyone,,0,0,0,,O kanibaloch ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:32.97,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Len...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.62,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,staré povesti o ľudožravích "obroch"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:41.21,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ale poznáš predsa príbehy o svätcoch ktorý boli len napoly ľuďmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:44.59,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Schádzali z hôr a unášali ľudí priamo na svoj stôl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:48.03,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,O-o čom to hovoríte?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.50,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ich obete...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.08,Anyone,,0,0,0,,boli pripútané ku stolu a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:55.74,Anyone,,0,0,0,,vykuchané tak ako sa dnes kuchajú ryby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:58.02,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ich vnútornosti potom nahádzali do rieky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:01.85,Anyone,,0,0,0,,To je skutočný význam slova "Watanagashi".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.98,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Sviatok Watanagashi ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:10.11,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Tu som si zapísala všetko čo som dokázala zistiť. Ak chceš, môžeš si ich prezrieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:13.21,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Obete rituálu pre Oyashira
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:16.58,Anyone,,0,0,0,,sú nakoniec utopené v Onigafuchiskom Močiari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.37,Anyone,,0,0,0,,V bezodnom močiari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:25.41,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Takže podla Vás sú všetci ľudia čo za tie roky zmizli
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:27.59,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,na dne toho močiara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:29.10,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To nie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.30,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}takže aj Satoshi...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.05,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Chceš sa pozrieť?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:40.02,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Kasai to si ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.31,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,To som ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.98,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Poď ďalej.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.78,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Máš to tu pekné.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:59.06,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ako to vyzerá vonku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:05:59.74,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nuž
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:04.28,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,nová škola je práve tak nudná ako som čakala,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.96,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,ale zapísala som si len minimum prednášok.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.38,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:14.68,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ruka sa ti už zahojila?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:18.35,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Rany sa už zahojili,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.06,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,ale stále je ich vidieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.85,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Stále ich pred každým skrývam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:26.44,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Je mi to ľúto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.19,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Neospravedlňuj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:32.36,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Správala si sa tak ako sa od teba čakalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.20,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nezazlievam ti to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:36.07,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.66,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.37,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Týmto je to odpustené.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.83,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Naozaj mi to všetko odpustíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.87,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Aj Satoshiho?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.97,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ja viem že si
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.34,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,ho mala rada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:57.20,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Napokon, pred celou rodinou som vášnivo vyhlásila som že ho milujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:01.88,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ale Oni-Baba naozaj verila že si ukázala svoju ľútosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.55,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ak by neverila bolo by to pre mňa zlé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.98,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Po tom všetkom ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:13.03,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Rada by som vedela kam vlastne išiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:16.96,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A práve vtedy sa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.87,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}vo mne zrodil démon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.07,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ah, prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:25.79,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ja naozaj neviem čo sa s ním stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.04,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Klameš.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.53,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Naozaj! Ani Oni-Baba to nevie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.27,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Klameš!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:31.84,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Klameš!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.88,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Klameš!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:40.45,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,To ty si uniesla Satoshiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:42.20,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ty a celá vaša prekliata rodina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.89,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ty! Ty!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:46.30,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Vráť mi ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:49.56,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Vráť mi môjho Satoshiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:56.44,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Mion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:57.39,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,To sú...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:01.08,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,také isté rany ako mám ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:08.16,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Pretože by to bolo nefér...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:10.88,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,...keby sa to stalo len tebe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:14.46,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Prečo len tebe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.63,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,...keď sme dvojčatá?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:18.72,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:25.60,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Kričala som na Oni-Babu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.56,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,aby nechala Satoshiho na pokoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:30.41,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,A ona povedala:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:33.15,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,"Ukáž mi svoju ľútosť a porozmýšľam o tom."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:38.44,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Preto by ste obaja mohli žiť ako normálny ľudia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:40.60,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.32,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ale Satoshi zmizol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.41,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Shion, ver mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:51.29,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ja naozaj neviem prečo zmizol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.36,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Mion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:58.97,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Odpusť... Bolelo to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.17,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Shion...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:04.10,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Teba to určite bolelo viac.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:09.04,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prikázala som tomu démonovi vo mne{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:10.73,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aby veril Mion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:16.53,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A pritom som odložila všetky city k Satoshimi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.99,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}až na samé dno svojho srdca.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:29.25,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ďalší rok prešiel bez problémov.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.00,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Až do toho dňa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:34.08,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:36.59,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,'šlaka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.71,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Prečo parkujú tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:43.47,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Opla.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.43,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Daja vu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:52.72,Anyone,,0,0,0,,............... .....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.15,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je to presne také isté...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:58.94,Anyone,,0,0,0,,.. .. .. ..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:01.84,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Dajte jej pokoj!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:04.82,Anyone,,0,0,0,,A ty si kto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.33,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Satoshi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:19.28,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Zmizni odtiaľto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:22.08,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Chceš aj ty jednu dostať?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:22.84,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Haaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:26.15,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Emmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.76,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Počkajte, počkajte! Netreba žiadne násilie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.02,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Drž hubu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:38.29,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Maebara-san, zavolali sme všetkých!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:40.38,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Kurva to je zlé!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:41.15,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Padáme!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.82,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:45.64,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Mion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:49.36,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Neboj sa, nikomu nepoviem že si sa tu takmer rozplakala.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:51.20,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,No tak, preber sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:59.05,SText1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\i1}Deja vu, vyslovované {\c&HFFFFFF&}dežavú{\c},\Nje francúzsky výraz pre pocit\N"že toto sa mi už raz stalo."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:04.01,SText2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\i1}Obecne sa pokladá aj\Nza chybu v Matrixe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:09.12,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Mion, teba sa ten Kei-chan naozaj páči, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:09.91,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Takže,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:12.56,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,skús jeho osobnosť popísať jediným slovom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.36,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Tak teda...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.73,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,...je zábavný!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:21.52,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Na našom poslednom kľubovom stretnutí,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.80,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,bolo to v hračkárstve,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.48,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mion mi povedala{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:26.22,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}že sa ten chlapec volá Keiichi Maebara.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.76,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je od nás o rok mladší.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:31.39,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A len pred nedávnom sa prisťahoval.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.70,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mion ho má veľmi rada.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.42,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,...a potom,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:41.36,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,pretože boli Keiichim naozaj nadšený,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:44.29,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,mu strýko venoval bábiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.71,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,A ty si ju chcela?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:49.30,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Áno, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.01,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan ju nedal mne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.68,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Povedal: "Nemyslím že by sa k tebe hodila..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.18,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Dal ju Rene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.53,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Chcela by som začať znova.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:02.82,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Chcela by som zase začať od dňa keď som ho prvý raz stretla
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:06.01,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,a ukázať mu že som tiež dievča.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:08.19,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Mion, berieš to príliš vážne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:10.53,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ešte vždy to môžeš napraviť!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.28,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nieje predsa medzi vami priepasť.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:17.39,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Neprežeň to, len buď prirodzená
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:18.75,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,a pomaly ho získaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:22.40,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,A hlavne vyšachuj tú Renu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.66,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ale Rena je tak strašne roztomilá!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:29.71,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ak máš rivalku, nestačí len upútať pozornosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:30.80,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Mion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:34.21,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Slzy dokážu chlapca prilákať,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.47,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,ale nedokážu ho udržať.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.96,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Musíš sa stále usmievať
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.60,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,a občas upustiť slzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.32,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Myslím že je to celkom pekný návod, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:47.87,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Možno by som to na ňom mohla skúsiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:50.92,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Eh? Nie... NIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.56,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Takže Mion,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:55.16,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,vyskúšame ktorej sa podarí získať Keiichiho?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:57.28,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nie, nie, nikdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:59.81,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Shion! Ak prídeš do Himanizawi, otočím ťa naspäť!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:01.71,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To je úžasné.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:01.71,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Nikdy! Rozumieš? Nikdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.52,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Ak sa len priblížiš, poženiem ťa späť.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:05.19,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ty môžeš mať strach o svojho chlapca... Závidím ti.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:09.84,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,On tu nieje...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.47,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,...pre mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:14.84,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,To nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:20.22,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikomu nebude vadiť že sa Mion a Kei-chan majú radi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.02,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nechcem im závidieť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.23,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nechcem žiarliť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:30.92,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nechcem aby mali problémy len pre to že som ich mala ja.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.53,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Už je to takmer rok odkedy Satoshi zmizol.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:40.31,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Za chvílu príde ďalší sviatok Watanagashi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.27,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Krátko na to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:46.27,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}si ma pomýlil z Mion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:50.10,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Držali sme sa za ruky keď sme narazili na Mion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:53.26,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A tak začala táto "roztržka".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:57.75,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Myslím že mám Keiichiho perverzností práve tak dosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.42,Rika,,0,0,0,,Je to muž, nemôže za to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:04.02,Rena,,0,0,0,,Mi-chan, Shi-chan, toto ho bolí!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.80,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Mion,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:10.31,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,budeme sa preťahovať až kým ho neroztrhneme?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:13.68,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Shion, ak prestaneš ťahať, problém sa vyrieši.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:16.11,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Proste sa zober a vráť sa do Okinomie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:16.82,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.03,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ako rozkážeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:23.54,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Takže Kei-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:27.49,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,zdá sa že ak budem sestru ešte trocha dráždiť, uhryzne ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.30,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Takže idem domov!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:30.67,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Shion,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.01,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,vieš,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.50,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,ďakujem za dnešok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:38.47,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,To nič nebolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:41.00,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Uvidíme sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:46.19,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Maj sa Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.02,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Už sa nevracaj"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.44,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Rena, ty budeš strážiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:50.30,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Satoko, ty nastav pasce!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.57,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,A Rika rozhádže soľ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:54.01,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnVerdana\fs49.5\pos(981,56.25)}Hádzanie soli v Japonsku symbolizuje odháňanie zlých duchov.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.23,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Odpusť mi, Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.71,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Odpusť mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.79,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nezabudla som na teba, Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.08,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nezabudla som.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:10.10,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Život bez teba je
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.90,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,šedivý, osamelí,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:14.23,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,a strašne nudný.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:16.06,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Uvidíme sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:19.20,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Vôbec to nebolo príjemné.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.64,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nebola som šťastná.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.35,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nenávidím toho drzého babráka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.97,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Satoshi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.04,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Satoshi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:35.49,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Satoshi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.16,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Satoshi-kun!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.17,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Kam si sa podel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.82,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Satoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:04.64,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,...kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:09.15,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Takže tam si bol.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.16,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.08,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Shion-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.80,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Takano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.89,Anyone,,0,0,0,,My sa asi ešte nepoznáme.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.29,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ja som Tomitake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:33.07,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ty budeš určite Mionino dvojča.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.03,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Rád ťa spoznávam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.39,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Počula som že ste výborný fotograf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.99,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Výborný... To trocha preháňaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.93,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Dávno som ťa nevidela som ťa v knižnici.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:49.27,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ako svojej nasledovníčke ti toho chcem veľa povedať.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.08,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Pokúsim sa prísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:56.51,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ale teraz by som mala ísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:00.03,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Budete sledovať Rikino predstavenie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:02.09,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Pravdu povediac,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:05.28,Anyone,,0,0,0,,plánujeme sa vplížiť do svätyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:09.83,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ako? Je tam zámok
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:11.26,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,a navyše je to zakázané.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:14.54,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Jirou je muž mnohých schopností.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:16.48,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ak chceš,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:18.42,Anyone,,0,0,0,,môžeš prísť za nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:20.18,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Takúto šancu by si nemala prepásť.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.16,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Svätyňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.39,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,plná nástrojov na mučenie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:31.60,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Možno sa tam dozviem čo sa stalo Satoshimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:37.90,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Bude to strašidelné ale ak by Kei-chan išiel so mnou...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:42.20,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Aj keby nás odhalili, Mion nás nechá utiecť.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:47.37,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Takže ma nevedieš na miesto z ktorého sa dá vidieť predstavenie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.66,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nič také som ani netvrdila.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:54.50,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Tomitake-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:10.06,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Toto je boh-ochranca Hinamizawi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.60,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Oyashiro-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:14.02,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oyashiro-sama{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:18.52,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ak si naozaj zničil Satoshiho, nikdy ti to neodpustím.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.11,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikdy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:22.61,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikdy ti to neodpustím.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:30.36,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ak je to čo vravela Takano pravda,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:32.53,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ten krutý rituál{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:35.95,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sa odohráva dodnes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.72,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Satoshi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.46,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Si to ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:57.56,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Si to naozaj ty, Satoshi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:02.21,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,To nieje on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:07.49,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.58,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Zľakla si sa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:14.58,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Mimochodom, dnes v noci na niekoho dopadne Oyashirova kliatba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:18.88,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oni to nepočujú?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.91,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Predstavenie práve skončilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.43,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fs135\shad0\bord0\fr-90\pos(1209,540)\c&H2F704F&}Sonozaki
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:03.05,Anyone,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE0FDDC&}S tým nič nenarobíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:07.54,Anyone,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE0FDDC&}Ten mladý zašiel priďaleko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:08.75,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Súhlasím.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:12.37,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Je jasné že vyvolal Oyashirov hnev.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.98,Anyone,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE0FDDC&}Polícia to vyšetruje
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:17.36,Anyone,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE0FDDC&}ale my vieme kto to spravil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.18,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Zdá sa že to bola Takano.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:24.81,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vyvolal Oyashirov hnev?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:29.70,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vyšetruje to polícia? Takano?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.32,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dnes sa to predsa stalo znova.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:37.04,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Už piaty raz. Oyashirova kliatba!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:40.07,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale prečo Mion a Oni-Baba{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:43.00,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}rozprávajú o Oyashirovom hneve?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:48.42,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oni vedia že sme sa vlámali do svätyne!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:01.69,Rena,,0,0,0,,Mi-chan, tebe sa to ešte nestalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:05.91,Rena,,0,0,0,,Počuješ kroky ktoré idú za tebou ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.74,Rena,,0,0,0,,V noci sa to vznáša nad tvojím vankúšom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.61,Rena,,0,0,0,,a pozerá na teba ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:14.43,Rena,,0,0,0,,Niekto ťa potichu pozoruje ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:16.30,Rena,,0,0,0,,Niekto kto je stále s tebou ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.76,Rena,,0,0,0,,To je to čo Satoshi cíti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:22.86,Rena,,0,0,0,,Je to znamenie Oyashirovej kliatby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:25.74,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takže{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:26.50,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}čo je to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:29.56,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čo je to čo sa za mnou plíži{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:32.29,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,{\i1}odkedy som vošla do svätyne?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:10.51,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}To get my happiness I had done everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:10.51,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Pre to aby som mohla byť šťastná som už spravila všetko,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:16.89,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}but had done nothing to be blamed and accused of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:16.89,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}ale nespravila som nič za čo by si ma mohol súdiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:23.44,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}The sounds of footsteps became louder every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:23.44,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Zvuk krokov sa každým dňom zdal byť o kúsok bližšie,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:30.57,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Then I noticed the fact there was no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:30.57,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}až som si uvedomila že môj čas vypršal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:38.75,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}I was a believer in life to be myself always,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:38.75,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Vždy som verila že môj život patrí iba mne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:45.71,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}and was asking whether I would be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:45.71,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}a pýtala som sa ho, či ešte môžem žiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:52.76,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Give me a reason why not to adopt in this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:52.76,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Tak mi daj dôvod prečo nejsť svojou cestou,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:23:00.10,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}or judge me to be guilty of so many incurable sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:23:00.10,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}alebo ma súď za všetky moje hriechy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:06.99,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Tell me why, or why not. Complainig way too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:06.99,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Povedz prečo alebo prečo nie, lebo zatiaľ čo som plakala,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:15.12,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}maybe I overlooked something fatal for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:15.12,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}musela som prehliadnuť niečo strašné.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:19.68,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Hladal si len malú útechu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:23.47,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Opäť ťa ale pohltil kruh nenávisti.
